title: Federal Bureau of Physics (001(Collider) - 012) (2013 - Ongoing)
description:
Federal Bureau of Physics (001(Collider) - 012) (2013 - Ongoing) (Digital) (Nahga-Empire) 



A sci-fi Vertigo series from writer Simon Oliver and artist Robbi Rodriguez.

The title was previously known as Collider, but ran into copyright issues, and had to change its name with the second issue. The first issue of Collider was reprinted as FBP: Federal Bureau of Physics #1 after the release of the second issue.
